## ⚠️ CRITICAL — REPEATED AT BOTTOM

Top causes of broken Rocket projects (in order):
1. **Missing migration push** → tables don't exist → everything fails silently
2. **Supabase project paused** → free tier, 7-day inactivity → restore at supabase.com
3. **getSession() in server code** → auth appears to work but is insecure and breaks on refresh
4. **middleware.ts in wrong location** → sessions never refresh → auth breaks after token expires
5. **Missing redirect URLs in Supabase** → auth works locally, broken after deploy
6. **Social OAuth on localhost** → will NEVER work — OAuth requires live URL
7. **Stripe raw body** → `request.json()` silently destroys webhook signature
8. **Env vars missing in Netlify** → app works locally, broken in production
9. **Missing profile trigger** → signup works, dashboard blank
10. **Stripe test/live isolation** → products don't transfer between modes
